Package com.poesys.db.dao.update

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IUpdate<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a data transfer object (DTO) in the database.
    IUpdateBatch<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a batch of data transfer objects (DTOs) in the database.
    IUpdateCollection<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface for a Command pattern class that updates a collection of data transfer objects (DTOs) in the database.
    IUpdateSql<T extends IDbDto>
    An interface that defines the set of operations required by an IUpdate, IUpdateBatch, or IUpdateCollection object to build a SQL UPDATE statement for a data transfer object (DTO).
    IUpdateWithParameters<P extends IDbDto>
    An interface for a Command-pattern class that updates a database based on a set of parameters contained in a data transfer object (DTO).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    UpdateBatchByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IUpdateBatch interface that contains the base code for updating a batch of objects in the database.
    UpdateByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IUpdate interface that updates a data transfer object (DTO) using a SQL statement defined in an IUpdateSql object, identifying the object in the database using the primary key of the DTO.
    UpdateCacheBatchByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateBatchByKey class that removes all the data transfer objects (DTOs) in the updated list from the DTO cache
    UpdateCacheByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateByKey class that removes the updated data transfer object (DTO) from the cache.
    UpdateCacheCollectionByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateCollectionByKey class that removes all the data transfer objects (DTOs) in the updated list from the DTO cache
    UpdateCollectionByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IUpdateCollection interface that contains the base code for updating a collection of objects in the database.
    UpdateMemcachedBatchByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateBatchByKey class that removes all the data transfer objects (DTOs) in the updated list from the DTO cache
    UpdateMemcachedByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateByKey class that removes the updated data transfer object (DTO) from the cache.
    UpdateMemcachedCollectionByKey<T extends IDbDto>
    A subclass of the UpdateCollectionByKey class that removes all the data transfer objects (DTOs) in the updated list from the DTO cache
    UpdateWithParameters<P extends IDbDto>
    An implementation of the IUpdateWithParameters interface that updates the database with a single UPDATE statement parameterized with the contents of a data transfer object (DTO).
